ogramming\n* [[Lady Antebellum]] \u2013 Featured Artist\n* Robert John \"Mutt\" Lange \u2013 Producer\n* Noah Passovoy \u2013 Additional Production, Composer, Engineer, Programming\n* Olle Romo \u2013 Engineer, Pro-Tools\n* Eric Ivan Rosse \u2013 Programming\n* Travis Schneider \u2013 Photography\n* Mike Shipley \u2013 Engineer, Mixing\n* Shawn Tellez \u2013 Composer\n* Brian Wohlgemuth \u2013 Assistant, Pro-Tools\n\nBased on the liner notes of ''Hands All Over'', A&M Octone Records.\n\n==Chart performance==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2010\u201311)\n!Peak<br/>position \n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|7|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|20|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|48|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|21|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|5|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Denmark|20|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|8|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n|[[European Top 100 Albums]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/charts/european-albums?tag=relcharts|title=Billboard - Music Charts, News, Photos & Video|author=|date=|website=billboard.com|accessdate=16 April 2018}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|7\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|46|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|16|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany|17|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Greece|7|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Hungary|18|year=2012|week=8|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|