e\n| length13 = 3:14\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n;Maroon 5\n* [[Adam Levine]] \u2013 lead vocals, guitar\n* [[Jesse Carmichael]] \u2013 keyboards, guitar, backing vocals\n* [[Mickey Madden]] \u2013 bass guitar\n* [[James Valentine (musician)|James Valentine]] \u2013 lead and rhythm guitar, backing vocals\n* [[Matt Flynn (musician)|Matt Flynn]] \u2013 drums, percussion\n\n;Additional personnel\n* Denika Bedrossian \u2013 Grooming\n* [[Brad Blackwood]] \u2013  Mastering\n* [[Bruce Bouton]] \u2013 Guitar\n* Lenny Castro \u2013 Percussion\n* Aristotle Circa \u2013 Wardrobe\n* Scott Cooke \u2013 Editing\n* Autumn de Wilde \u2013 Photography\n* Lauren Dukoff \u2013 Portrait Photography\n* Isha Erskine \u2013 Engineer\n* Davis Factor \u2013 Portrait Photography\n* [[Sam Farrar]] \u2013 Additional Production, Composer, Engineer, Programming\n* Rosie Hardy \u2013 Back Cover Photo, Cover Photo\n* Kelly Henson \u2013 Grooming\n* Chad Hugo \u2013 Programming\n* [[Lady Antebellum]] \u2013 Featured Artist\n* Robert John \"Mutt\" Lange \u2013 Producer\n* Noah Passovoy \u2013 Additional Production, Composer, Engineer, Programming\n* Olle Romo \u2013 Engineer, Pro-Tools\n* Eric Ivan Rosse \u2013 Programming\n* Travis Schneider \u2013 Photography\n* Mike Shipley \u2013 Engineer, Mixing\n* Shawn Tellez \u2013 Composer\n* Brian Wohlgemuth \u2013 Assistant, Pro-Tools\n\nBased on the liner notes of ''Hands All Over'', A&M Octone Records.\n\n==Chart performance==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2010\u201311)\n!Peak<br/>position \n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|7|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|20|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|48|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|21|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|5|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Denmark|20|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|8|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n|[[European Top 100 Albums]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/charts/european-albums?tag=relcharts|title=Billboard - Music Charts, News, Photos & Video|author=|date=|website=billboard.com|accessdate=16 April 2018}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|7\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|46|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|16|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany|17|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Greece|7|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Hungary|18|year=2012|week=8|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Ireland|13|year=2011|week=36|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Italy|10|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n|[[Oricon|Japanese Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/ |title=\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0 \u9031\u9593\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0-ORICON STYLE \u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 |publisher=Oricon.co.jp |date=2008-04-30 |accessdate=2010-12-03}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|-\n{{albumchart|Mexico|19|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|New Zealand|12|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Poland|49|id=609|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Portugal|18|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Spain|23|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All Over|accessdate=2013-04-12}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Sweden|50|artist=Maroon 5|album=Hands All