ertifiedawards/search.aspx ]</ref>\n| 413,034<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mediaor.com/post/96960685144/official-charts-analysis-sam-smith-sales-cant|title=Official Charts Analysis: Sam Smith sales can't hide dismal week for albums|last=Jones|first=Alan|date=8 September 2014|work=[[Music Week]]|publisher=Intent Media|accessdate=7 June 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| United States ([[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]])\n|Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?content_selector=gold-platinum-searchable-database |title=Gold & Platinum Searchable Database \u2013 July 23, 2013 |publisher=RIAA |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23}}</ref>\n| 1,400,000\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Region\n! Date\n! [[Record Label|Label]]\n! Format\n|-\n| Japan<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B003UDP8Y2 |title=Hands All Over: Maroon 5: Amazon.co.jp: \u97f3\u697d |publisher=Amazon.co.jp}}</ref>\n| September 15, 2010\n| [[Universal Music Group|Universal International]]\n| rowspan=\"10\"|{{Flat list|\n* [[Compact disc|CD]]\n* [[Music download|digital download]]}}\n|-\n| South Korea<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cooltrack.co.kr/shop/shopdetail.html?branduid=23343 |title=Maroon 5 - Hands All Over (Standard Edition) (\ud3ec\uc2a4\ud130+\uc9c0\uad00\ud1b5 \ubb34\ub8cc\uc99d\uc815) |website=Cooltrack |accessdate=September 21, 2017}}</ref>\n| September 16, 2010\n| [[Universal Music Group|Universal Music]]\n|-\n| Germany<ref name=\"Amazon.de\">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/dp/B003Y3J0RE |title=Hands All Over: Maroon 5: Amazon.de: Musik |publisher=Amazon.de |date=2009-09-09 |accessdate=2010-08-06}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"|September 17, 2010\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[A&M Octone Records|A&M Octone]]\n|-\n| Austria<ref name=\"Amazon.de\"/>\n|-\n| Switzerland<ref name=\"Amazon.de\"/>\n|-\n| Australia<ref name=\"AUS\">{{cite web |url=http://www.sanity.com.au/products/2189972/Hands_All_Over |title=Hands All Over \u2013 Maroon 5