 for Women, Alappuzha]]<ref>[http://www.stjosephcollegeforwomen.com/ SJCW]</ref> \n*St. Michael's college, [[Cherthala]]<ref>SMC {{cite web|url=http://www.keralauniversity.edu/stmicheals.htm |title=Archived copy |accessdate=18 February 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527094214/http://www.keralauniversity.edu/stmicheals.htm |archivedate=27 May 2010 }}</ref> \n*[[T. K. Madhava Memorial College]]<ref>\"TKM {{cite web|url=http://www.keralauniversity.edu/tkmadava.htm |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2016-02-18 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926212337/http://www.keralauniversity.edu/tkmadava.htm |archivedate=26 September 2011 |df=dmy }}\"</ref> \n*St. Aloysius college Edathua<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aloysiuscollege.org/ |title=St Aloysius |publisher=Aloysiuscollege.org |date= |accessdate=2013-09-25}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n*[[Alappuzha East]]\n*[[Alappuzha West]]\n*[[List of people from Alappuzha]]\n*[[Travancore Labour Association]]\n*[[Technical Higher Secondary School, Cherthala]], Pallippuram\n*[[Ernakulam-Kayamkulam coastal railway line]]\n*[[KCA Cricket Stadium, Alappuzha]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n* {{cite news\n|author=fallingrain\n|url=http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/13/Alappuzha.html\n|title=Alappuzha geographic location\n|accessdate=June 4, 2011}}\n* {{cite news\n|author=msnindia\n|url=http://weather.in.msn.com/local.aspx?wealocations=wc:INXX0004&q=Alleppey%2C+Kerala\n|title=Alappuzha annual weather\n|accessdate=June 4, 2011\n|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110902013228/http://weather.in.msn.com/local.aspx?wealocations=wc:INXX0004&q=Alleppey,+Kerala\n|archive-date=2 September 2011\n|url-status=dead\n}}\n* {{cite news\n|author=holidayso\n|url=https://holidayso.in/alleppey-Tour-package\n|title=Alappuzha \u2013 Venice of the East\n|accessdate=July 7, 2017\n\n}}\n\n[[backwaters of alappuzha|https://alteredgoal.com/https-alteredgoal-com-backwaters-of-alappuzha/]]== Exte